data.description: Welcome to sought after Buckhead's Walden on Lenox community! This well-designed roommate floorplan condo features 3 bedrooms, 2 Baths, open living room with a cozy fireplace and hardwood floors, seamlessly connected to a separate dining room, a light-filled bonus room adjacent to the kitchen boasts dual skylights, providing versatility as an office or family room. Enhancing privacy, the stylish barn doors can be closed for a polished look. The kitchen boast beautiful granite countertops, robust cabinets with ample storage with a dedicated pantry. Additional storage in the laundry room. The master suite offers a generously-sized walk-in closet and French doors leading to the balcony. The gated community has ample guest parking, a large pool, clubhouse, gym, and nature trail leading to Shady Valley park that features playgrounds, dog parks, basketball, and tennis courts. Wifi, water, cable, trash & recycling are included in HOA dues. This is the perfect location in Buckhead just minutes from I85, US 400, shopping plazas, outstanding restaurants, public transportation, Lenox Mall and Phipps Plaza!
